parcel.description: Join @punk4156, @metaverseDAO and @AccelerateArt for the inaugural exhibition of work from the esteemed 4156 collection. Featuring a live tour of the 4156 Crypovoxels exhibition, 11 new ape-themed portraits that are to be auctioned on OpenSea. Each participating artist received 90% of the proceeds from the sale of their work, with 10% going to the organizers of the exhibition. built by @Gareth
